Implement bubble sort.
Time complexity: O(V+E)
```python
def bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(0, n-i-1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:
                arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]
    return arr
```

Write a Python function to flatten nested list.
```python
def flatten(nested):
    result = []
    for item in nested:
        if isinstance(item, list):
            result.extend(flatten(item))
        else:
            result.append(item)
    return result
```

